StPidAmpMaker - STAR PID Amplitude Maker

This code is based on Richard's FORTRAN version of PID package.
The C++ version is written by Aihong Tang.

Thanks Weiming for his help for the former version of the code. 

Care taker of the code:  Aihong Tang.


For documentation see doc/ directory, or see
http://www.rhic.bnl.gov/~aihong/StPidAmpMakerDocument/

